Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
28 July 2011	cnwer1	Initial creation CCMS MES 1033

*/

vars

begin
	
	self.doComboBayIdBuild();
	self.doComboDeckIdBuild();
epilog

end;</source>
